import React from 'react'
import "./input.css"

const fN = document.querySelector("label > .fn");
fN.addEventListener("keydown", function(event){

  if(event.keyCode === 13){
    let answerFN = document.querySelector("label > .fn").value
    console.log(answerFN)
  }
})
 


const Input =()=> {
  return (<>
  <label>First Name
  <input className='fn' />
  </label>

  <label>Last Name
  <input className='ln'/>
  </label>

  <label>Email
  <input className='email'/>
  </label>

  <label>Phone
  <input className='phone'/>
  </label>

  <label>Password
  <input className='password'/>
  </label>
  
  <label>Confirm Password
  <input className='confpass'/>
  </label>

  </>)
}
export default Input;
